<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA84">
<l>vāḻtti yavaṉaṭiyaip pūppuṉaintu niṉṟalaiyait</l>
<l>tāḻttirukai kūppeṉṟāṟ kūppāta pāḻttaviti</l>
<l>yeṅkuṟṟā yeṉṟavaṉai yēttāteṉ ṉeñcamē</l>
<l>taṅkattā ṉāmēlun taṅku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [I] say “praise, adorn his feet with flowers, lower your head,</l>
<l>fold [your] two hands”, they do not fold. Rules in ruin,</l>
<l>without praising him “where have you been?”, my heart,</l>
<l>ieven if it is staying, stay.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
